scripts.build-dev: git checkout master && git pull && DISABLE_ESLINT_PLUGIN=true env-cmd -f .env.development refine build && wrangler pages deploy --project-name finsquid-auth-sdk-dev --branch master ./build
scripts.build-stage: git checkout staging && git pull && DISABLE_ESLINT_PLUGIN=true env-cmd -f .env.staging refine build && wrangler pages deploy --project-name finsquid-auth-sdk-staging --branch staging ./build
scripts.build-prod: git checkout production && git pull && DISABLE_ESLINT_PLUGIN=true env-cmd -f .env.production refine build && wrangler pages deploy --project-name finsquid-auth-sdk --branch production ./build
